cs.LO, cs.IT, cs.QI, cs.DS, cs.CC

The paper deals with the use of 2-categorical technology for describing and reasoning about complex quantum procedures, which involves aspects of logic (cs.LO), information theory (cs.IT), quantum information (cs.QI), data structures (cs.DS), and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper also references previous work in categorical quantum mechanics, which is closely related to category theory and logic. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO, followed by cs.IT, cs.QI, cs.DS, and cs.CC.
